_sText:
New 1.6 port I've been working on all morning. Map is intended for autobhop playstyle.
I kinda took on this map as a project to challenge myself to learn a bit more about Hammer while using good mapping practices. I also wanted to see if I still had what it takes to produce a decent quality map, as it's been a long while since my last update. A lot of effort went into this but I think it paid off in the end. 

Hope you enjoy it!
